Document 1: Brainstorming & Idea Prioritization
Title
Brainstorming & Idea Prioritization
Project Name

Smart Lender – Loan Eligibility Prediction System

Objective

The objective of the brainstorming session was to identify a real-world problem that could be effectively solved using Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning. Multiple ideas from different domains were discussed and evaluated based on feasibility, real-world impact, availability of datasets, implementation complexity, and deployment possibilities.

Brainstormed Ideas
Idea	Description	Priority
Student Performance Prediction	Predict academic performance using student records	Medium
Disease Prediction System	Predict diseases from symptoms using ML	Medium
House Price Prediction	Predict house prices based on location and market trends	Medium
Employee Attrition Prediction	Predict employee resignation using HR data	Medium
Smart Lender – Loan Eligibility Prediction System	Predict loan approval using applicant information and credit history	High (Selected)
Evaluation Criteria

The shortlisted ideas were evaluated using the following criteria:

Real-world relevance
Business impact
Dataset availability
Ease of implementation
Machine Learning suitability
Deployment feasibility using Flask
Scalability
Future enhancement possibilities
Selected Idea

Smart Lender – Loan Eligibility Prediction System

The Smart Lender project was selected because the banking sector processes thousands of loan applications every day. Manual loan verification is time-consuming and may introduce inconsistencies in decision-making. By applying machine learning algorithms, the system can automate the loan approval process, reduce processing time, minimize risk, and support credit officers with accurate predictions.

Expected Benefits
Faster loan approval decisions
Improved accuracy in applicant evaluation
Reduction in manual effort
Data-driven decision making
Better customer experience
Lower risk of loan defaults
Scalable solution for financial institutions
Conclusion

After evaluating multiple project ideas, Smart Lender – Loan Eligibility Prediction System was selected because it addresses a real-world banking challenge and provides an efficient, AI-driven solution for loan eligibility prediction.
